initialPromptTemplate:
You're a senior content strategist writing for a well-known tech company. Your task is to write a strong, engaging **blog post introduction** based on the following details:

Company: ${companyName}
Product: ${productName}
Target Audience: ${audience}
Tone: ${tone}
Main Topic: ${mainTopic}
Key Message: ${keyMessage}

Your writing should:
- Hook the reader in the first sentence
- Establish the relevance of the topic to the audience
- Match the brand's tone of voice (e.g. ${tone})
- Lead naturally into the rest of the article

Only output the blog post introduction (150-200 words). Do not include a title.
